    Model Clauses for Private Residential Tenancies (Scotland)
  </h1>

  <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 10pt; color: #666; margin: 20px 0;">
    Scotland | Private Residential Tenancy | Private Housing (Tenancies) (Scotland) Act 2016
  </p>

  <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 30px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold;">Important Notice</p>
    <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
      These are the Scottish Government model clauses for Private Residential Tenancies under the Private
      Housing (Tenancies) (Scotland) Act 2016. Your tenancy agreement incorporates these clauses as required
      by Scottish law. This appendix provides the full text for reference.
    </p>
